snippet.title: Mordfield Command  |  Official Trailer | Turn-based Strategy
snippet.description:
Mankind's greatest creation has become its deadliest enemy. In this tactical turn-based strategy game, lead humanity's last resistance against the AI forces that have conquered Earth. Every move counts in your desperate fight to reclaim our world from the machines.
🎮 Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2948470/Mordfield_Command/
📱 Follow us: instagram.com/mordfield_command/
🔔 Subscribe for updates!
